        - Make IDublinCore.tags a patch field
          [vangheem]
        
        - Add `appendunique` and `extendunique` to patch field operations
          [vangheem]
        
        
        4.8.16 (2019-07-24)
        -------------------
        
        - Fix exhausted retries conflict error response
          [vangheem]
        
        
        4.8.15 (2019-07-23)
